<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f3f4f6;">
  <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="background-color: #f3f4f6;">
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
        <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
          <tr>
            <td style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6b7280 0%, #4b5563 100%); padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;">
              <h1 style="margin: 0; color: #ffffff; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700;">Account Deleted</h1>
              <p style="margin: 8px 0 0; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); font-size: 14px;">Your Pet Haven Hub Account Has Been Removed</p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 40px 30px;">
              <h2 style="margin: 0 0 20px; color: #1f2937; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600;">
                We're Sorry to See You Go
              </h2>
              <p style="margin: 0 0 24px; color: #4b5563; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
                Your Pet Haven Hub account has been permanently deleted. All your personal information
                has been securely removed from our systems.
              </p>
              <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="background-color: #f9fafb; border-radius: 6px; border-left: 4px solid #6b7280; margin-bottom: 30px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding: 20px;">
                    <p style="margin: 0 0 12px; color: #1f2937; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">WHAT WAS DELETED</p>
                    <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8;">
                      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Your account profile and login credentials</li>
                      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Your personal information and preferences</li>
                      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Your adoption request history</li>
                      <li>All associated data</li>
                    </ul>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
              <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="background-color: #fef3c7; border-radius: 6px; border-left: 4px solid #d97706; margin-bottom: 30px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding: 20px;">
                    <p style="margin: 0 0 8px; color: #92400e; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">📋 DATA RETENTION</p>
                    <p style="margin: 0; color: #92400e; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">
                      We retain aggregated, anonymized data for legal compliance and system administration.
                      Your personal information is not recoverable.
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
              <p style="margin: 0 0 12px; color: #1f2937; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">We'd Love Your Feedback</p>
              <p style="margin: 0; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">
                If you'd like to tell us why you left or have suggestions for improvement, please reply
                to this email or contact us at
                <a href="mailto:<%= ENV.fetch('ADMIN_EMAIL', 'support@pethavenhub.com') %>" style="color: #4F46E5; text-decoration: none;"><%= ENV.fetch('ADMIN_EMAIL', 'support@pethavenhub.com') %></a>
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
              <p style="margin: 0 0 12px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">
                <strong style="color: #1f2937;">Pet Haven Hub</strong><br>
                Panauti, Kathmandu, Nepal
              </p>
              <p style="margin: 0 0 12px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 12px;">
                © <%= Time.current.year %> Pet Haven Hub. All rights reserved.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
